<HEADLINE>
<P>
THANKSGIVING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Closed Thursday: All government offices, courts, banks, post offices, stock and 
commodity exchanges, libraries, schools and many businesses. RTD buses will 
follow Sunday schedules. Closed Friday: Schools and all city, county and state 
offices, courts and libraries. 
</P>
<P>
Open Friday: Federal courts and offices, post offices, banks, stock and 
commodity exchanges. RTD buses will follow regular schedules. 
</P>
</TEXT>
