STATES -- POLITICS; WOMENS RIGHTS; MAHER, LEO T; KILLEA, LUCY; RIGHT TO LIFE; 
SEPARATION OF CHURCH AND STATE; CATHOLICS; POLITICIANS; POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS 
</P>
