<SUBJECT>
<P>
BASKETBALL PLAYERS; LEWIS, TOM; PEPPERDINE UNIVERSITY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA112289-0080 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 138362 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 22, 1989, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 1; Column 5; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
