Fullerton; John Burns, Saddleback; Estrus Crayton, Rancho Santiago; Daryl 
McChristian, Riverside. WR: Cameron Lymon, Riverside; Paul Peters, Rancho 
Santiago; Mike Thomas, Fullerton. OL: Jason Downs, Riverside; Matt Nicolo, 
Fullerton; Mike Edge, Riverside; Mark Fely, Orange Coast; Mike Jepsen, Golden 
West; Vince Rollins, Riverside. TE: Rob Coons, Fullerton; Joe Dantuono, 
Riverside; Shane Talbert, Orange Coast. K: Eric Lange, Fullerton. P: Kevin 
Leon, Fullerton. 
</P>
